
- GENERAL -

ALT + F4 : Quit
ALT + ENTER : Fullscreen / windowed
ESC : Return to the last menu


- CONSTRUCTION MODE -

RIGHT CLICK         : Move camera
SCROLL WHEEL        : Zoom camera
Q/D                 : Rotate camera
SHIFT + SCROLL      : Change the maximum height visible
PAGE UP/DOWN        : Change the maxumum height visible by 8 steps
LEFT CLICK          : Place current block
A/E or LEFT/RIGHT   : Change current block
0/1/2/3/4 or TAB    : Change structure type
F                   : Toggle pipette tool
MIDDLE CLICK or ESC : Reset current floor/wall/volume
Z/S                 : Change highlight mode 
CTRL + SCROLL       : Change wall/volume height
UP / DOWN ARROWS    : Change meteo
F5                  : QuickSave
F9                  : QuickLoad
X                   : Toggle HUD

- DEBUG -

R  : Refresh rendering
P  : Refresh shaders
G  : Debug grid
H  : Print debug infos
F1 : Toggle Global Illumination
F2 : Toggle Ambiant Occlusion
F3 : Toggle Block Borders
F4 : Toggle Shadows
F6 : Toggle Bloom


